creator: Sir Walter Scott
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 10 recordings of Knight And Wamba by Sir Walter Scott. This was the Weekly Poetry project for January 24, 2016. Read in English by Bruce Kachuk; Brian Darby; clarinetcarrot; David Lawrence; Newgatenovelist; Gloria Fontaine; Greg Giordano; Lee Ann Howlett; Maria Kasper and Raj Singh. A fun poem with a great rhythm. ( Stav Nisser. ) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B Audiobook (9MB)
subject: librivox; audiobooks; humor; literature; ballad; courting
